{"type":"text","timestamp":1778980309327,"sessionID":"ses_1cc8399e9ffe5MJ58juVe42pjM","part":{"id":"prt_e337d210a001PbmwNkb6nTJZ43","messageID":"msg_e337cf70b001nvtMwfMQuFj336","sessionID":"ses_1cc8399e9ffe5MJ58juVe42pjM","type":"text","text":"I’ve confirmed a minimal fix path: broaden `epiphyseal tract` to the `pineal complex` and drop the tetrapod-specific `innervated_by obturator nerve` axiom from the generic `adductor muscle of hip`. I’m checking out just those terms into `terms/` now so I can edit the small stanzas instead of the full ontology file.","time":{"start":1778980299018,"end":1778980309325}}}
